'''王彤文'''（{{bd|1967年||}}），英文名为 Lotus King Weiss，[[江苏|江苏]][[无锡|无锡]]人，现为美籍[[华裔|华裔]]公民，政治活跃家。

== 学术背景 ==
1984年考入[[上海第一醫科大學|上海第一醫科大學]]（現名[[復旦大学|復旦大学]]醫學院）醫學系讀本科，1988年在[[美国|美国]][[佛罗里达大学|佛罗里达大学]]解剖[[细胞生物学|细胞生物学]]系[[分子生物学|分子生物学]]及發生生物學专业攻读[[博士|博士]][[学位|学位]]。1992年获得[[博士|博士]][[学位|学位]]后，在[[波士顿|波士顿]]麻省總院，[[哈佛大学|哈佛大学]]醫學院做[[博士後|博士後]]研究，並開始從事[[癌症|癌症]]方面的基礎研究。

1994年，时年27岁的王彤文成為[[哈佛大学|哈佛大学]]講師，并于1997年擔任该校助理教授。在哈佛工作期间，王彤文拥有自己的研究室，並在包括《[[科学_(期刊)|科学]]》和《[[细胞_(期刊)|细胞]]》等一流的生物科技学雜誌上發表多篇文章。王彤文曾被聘任為Pfizer公司和其他生物技術公司的技術顧問，多次在[[美国|美国]]和國際會議上作學術報告。<ref>{{cite news |title=New York Times: Who is Fethullah Gulen? |url=https://dianeravitch.net/2016/07/16/new-york-times-who-is-fethullah-gulen/comment-page-1/ |accessdate=2021-10-25 |work=Diane Ravitch |date=2016-07-16 |language=en}}</ref>2002年，王彤文的研究室获得美国癌症研究协会（American Cancer Society ）100万美元的研究撥款。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nolanchart.com/article8652-dissidents-seek-to-derail-the-nomination-of-gary-locke-for-us-ambassador.html|title=Dissidents seek to derail the nomination of Gary Locke for U.S. ambassador , USA |first=Kusumi|last=John |work=Nolan Chart |date=12 May 2011-05-12 |accessdate=2013-04-02|quote=That year, the American Cancer Society awarded a grant of $1 million to Dr. Weiss' laboratory.}}</ref>2012年，王彤文与[[生物学|生物学]]研究者Johnson AR, Lao S, Galanko JA, Zeisel SH共同在著名的《PLOS ONE》（公共科學文庫期刊）网站上发表[[生物学|生物学]]研究性文章''Choline Dehydrogenase Polymorphism rs12676 Is a Functional Variation and Is Associated with Changes in Human Sperm Cell Function''。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache%3AfFiM4m2X77sJ%3Ahttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.plosone.org%2Farticle%2Finfo%3Adoi%2F10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0036047%2Bdr+tongwen+wang&hl=zh-CN&gbv=2&ct=clnk|title=Choline Dehydrogenase Polymorphism rs12676 Is a Functional Variation and Is Associated with Changes in Human Sperm Cell Function,  Obama|first=Gemmell|last=Neil John|work=PLOS|date=April 27, 2012-04-27|accessdate=2013-04-03|quote=Johnson AR, Lao S, Wang T, Galanko JA, Zeisel SH (2012) Choline Dehydrogenase Polymorphism rs12676 Is a Functional Variation and Is Associated with Changes in Human Sperm Cell Function. PLoS ONE 7(4): e36047. doi:10.1371/journal.pone.0036047.|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130422153202/http://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:fFiM4m2X77sJ:http://www.plosone.org/article/info:doi/10.1371/journal.pone.0036047%2Bdr+tongwen+wang&hl=zh-CN&gbv=2&ct=clnk|archivedate=2013年4月22日}}</ref>

2002年，王彤文开始使用西医技术手段研究[[法轮功|法轮功]]对人类免疫系统的影响。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nolanchart.com/article8652-dissidents-seek-to-derail-the-nomination-of-gary-locke-for-us-ambassador.html |title=Dissidents seek to derail the nomination of Gary Locke for U.S. ambassador , USA |first=Kusumi|last=John |work=Nolan Chart|date=12 May 2011-05-12 |accessdate=2013-04-02|quote=In 2002, Weiss undertook research to investigate human immune system responses to the practice of Falun Gong -- research that would use the techniques of Western medicine to perhaps vindicate the reported health benefits of practicing Falun Gong and advance cancer research.}}</ref>。

据[[纽约每日新闻报|纽约每日新闻报]]2013年3月6日报道，王彤文试图于2012年重新开办“全象特许学校”，该申请被纽约州教育部门否决。教育部门在回信中说申请手续不全。王彤文认为，申请被否决的原因是歧视[[法轮功|法轮功]]学员。纽约州立大学特许学校协会的发言人Elizabeth Genco说，该协会在审核这些申请办学时要“看它的创始团队是否具有开办一个有学习氛围的、有财务保障的和法律上声名良好的特许学校的意愿、技能和能力”。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/new-york/queens/falun-gong-follower-behind-attempt-open-charter-schools-article-1.1281217#ixzz2PCEMqr00|title=Falun Gong follower behind attempt to open six charter schools，New York|first=Trapasso|last=Clare|work=NEW YORK DAILY NEWS |date=6 March 2013-03-06 |accessdate=2013-04-02|quote=Her attempt to open the Whole Elephant Charter School, a Flushing boarding school for unwanted kids of Chinese immigrants, was shot down last year by the state Department of Education. The agency said in a letter her application was incomplete.Weiss, who used to go by the name Tongwen Wang, said that wasn’t true.
“Our application was not reviewed because of discrimination against me as a Falun Gong practitioner,” said Weiss, who previously said she had been arrested for trespassing and unjustly diagnosed with manic depression because of her beliefs.SUNY Charter Schools Institute spokeswoman Elizabeth Genco said the institute “seeks to determine if the founding group has the will, skill, and capacity to open an academically, fiscally, and legally sound charter” before it green lights a proposed school.}}</ref>

